0.7 18nov2023
* make logging work with weewx V3 or V4
* make this code work with python2 or python3
* use 'lightning_strike_count' and 'lightning_distance' instead of
  'lightning_strikes' and 'avg_distance'.  this means immediate compatiblity
  with the wview_extended schema.
* use data_services instead of the older process_services
* thanks to user roe-dl for these changes!

